{"word":"G5136 - τραχηλίζω - trachēlízō - trakh-ay-lid'-zo - Opened","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τραχηλίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">trachēlízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">trakh-ay-lid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Opened</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிர்வாணமாயும் வெளியரங்கமாயும் ஆக்குதல்"},{"paragraph":"1. to seize and twist the neck or throat"},{"paragraph":"2. to bend back the neck of the victim to be slain, to lay bare or expose by bending back"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5137 - τράχηλος - tráchēlos - trakh'-ay-los/5137\">G5137</a>; to <i>seize</i> by <i>the throat</i> or <i>neck</i>, that is, to <i>expose</i> the <i>gullet</i> of a victim for killing (generally to <i>lay bare</i>): - opened.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}